data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, & a convenient 2-stall attached garage.  Situated on a spacious lot, this property boasts a fenced-in yard providing privacy for outdoor activities.  Inside, the kitchen features modern appliances and ample cabinet space.  Retreat to the cozy nice sized bedrooms & main floor laundry. With its desirable features and prime location, this home offers comfortable living. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your new home sweet home!
